          	  <span class="gn13b">[1959-8 台灣教會公報 文類-詩 作者-周天來/Chiu Thian-lâi]</span>
          	            	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-9042.htm">一生讚美主 [ It-seng chàn-bí Chú ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12"> Normal   0      0   2      false   false   false                                                         MicrosoftInternetExplorer4   

